{"type":"text","timestamp":1775879389147,"sessionID":"ses_285588390ffes13MP8IEGHIZ9q","part":{"id":"prt_d7aa8a7b1001ZhPv1JDvmmGJr6","messageID":"msg_d7aa8969b001M5NQyYPgPloCev","sessionID":"ses_285588390ffes13MP8IEGHIZ9q","type":"text","text":"Now I have a comprehensive view of the AR-017 project. Let me provide a summary:\n\n---\n\n## Archive Summary: AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件\n\n### Project Info\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| **AR ID** | AR-017 |\n| **Title** | PicoD JWT 中间件 (JWT Middleware) |\n| **Module** | `pkg/picod/jwt` |\n| **Language** | Go |\n| **Size** | S (Small) |\n| **Status** | Partially Implemented |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Completed\n\n**Core Implementation (100% Complete):**\n\n| Component | File | Status |\n|-----------|------|--------|\n| Type Definitions | `pkg/picod/jwt/types.go` | ✅ Complete |\n| Error Definitions | `pkg/picod/jwt/errors.go` | ✅ Complete (9 error types) |\n| Token Validator | `pkg/picod/jwt/validator.go` | ✅ Complete |\n| HTTP Middleware | `pkg/picod/jwt/middleware.go` | ✅ Complete |\n| Configuration | `pkg/picod/jwt/config.go` | ✅ Complete |\n\n**Features Delivered:**\n\n1. **JWT Token Validation**\n   - HS256 (HMAC-SHA256) signature verification\n   - RS256 (RSA-SHA256) signature verification\n   - Token expiration validation with configurable clock skew\n   - Issuer claim validation\n   - Audience claim validation (optional)\n   - Not-before (`nbf`) claim validation\n   - Algorithm validation\n\n2. **HTTP Middleware**\n   - Bearer token extraction from Authorization header\n   - Standardized error responses (401/403 with JSON body)\n   - Claims injection into request context\n   - `GetClaims()` helper function\n   - `OptionalMiddleware()` for optional authentication\n\n3. **Configuration**\n   - Environment variable loading (`PICOD_JWT_*`)\n   - RSA public key loading from PEM files\n   - Clock skew configuration\n   - Multiple allowed algorithms support\n\n4. **Unit Tests (Validator)**\n   - `validator_test.go` - 34+ test cases covering:\n     - HS256/RS256 success and failure scenarios\n     - Expiration and clock skew validation\n     - Issuer and audience validation\n     - Malformed token handling\n     - Missing claims detection\n\n---\n\n### ⏸️ Deferred / Not Completed\n\n| Component | Status | Notes |\n|-----------|--------|-------|\n| **Middleware Unit Tests** | ❌ Missing | `middleware_test.go` not created |\n| **Integration Tests** | ❌ Missing | `integration_test.go` not created |\n| **Package GoDoc Examples** | ❌ Missing | Usage examples in godoc |\n| **Integration with AR-015** | ⏸️ Pending | Middleware not yet wired to PicoD command API |\n\n**Specific Deferred Tasks (from tasks.md):**\n\n- **ST-2.7** — Unit Tests (Middleware): 8 tasks not started\n  - `TestMiddleware_ValidToken`\n  - `TestMiddleware_MissingToken`\n  - `TestMiddleware_InvalidFormat`\n  - `TestMiddleware_InvalidSignature`\n  - `TestMiddleware_ExpiredToken`\n  - `TestMiddleware_InvalidIssuer`\n  - `TestMiddleware_ContextPropagation`\n\n- **ST-2.8** — Integration Tests: 3 tasks not started\n  - `TestIntegration_EndToEnd`\n  - Test helpers for token generation\n\n- **ST-2.9** — Documentation: 4 tasks partially complete\n  - Package-level GoDoc (basic comments present)\n  - Usage examples (missing)\n\n---\n\n### Completion Summary\n\n| Category | Tasks | Status |\n|----------|-------|--------|\n| **Core Implementation** | 26 tasks | ✅ 100% Complete |\n| **Validator Tests** | 9 tasks | ✅ 100% Complete |\n| **Middleware Tests** | 8 tasks | ❌ 0% Complete |\n| **Integration Tests** | 3 tasks | ❌ 0% Complete |\n| **Documentation** | 4 tasks | ⚠️ ~50% Complete |\n| **Overall** | **57 tasks** | **~65% Complete** |\n\n---\n\n### Key Technical Decisions\n\n1. **Library**: Uses `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5`\n2. **Algorithms**: HS256 (simple setups) and RS256 (production recommended)\n3. **Context Storage**: Private key pattern for claims in context\n4. **Error Mapping**: Library errors mapped to custom error types\n5. **Audience Support**: Added beyond original spec for flexibility","time":{"start":1775879389144,"end":1775879389144}}}
